data.name: HYDROPHILIC INTERMMITENT CATHETERS
data.description:
## COMPOSITION
- 100% PVC and 100% DEHP-FREE PVC
- hydrophilic coating Sachet

## STERILIZATION
- Ethylene Oxide (EO) Sterile

## PRESENTATIONS
- PVC and DEHP-FREE PVC
- Color-Coded Size Identification
- Male and Female
- Male Type: Standard and Tiemann Types

## PERFORMANCE
- Highly Slippery and Smoot Surface allowing successful introduction
